data.description: Better than new home for sale in Windy Pines Community of Torino. Homeowner has thought of every detail when putting the finishing touches on this home. Located in cul-de-sac sits beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home. Open floor plan with formal dining, living room and den that leads to screened patio with 2,200 gallon spa w/ waterfall that will sit 8 adults comfortably. Chef's kitchen with upgraded stainless steal appliances and wood cabinets. Split floor plan with cabana bath. Master suite has dual sinks, walk in shower is tiled, his and her walk in closets and custom lighting. Lush landscaping on the well manicured property. Firepit w/ pergola, security system and much more!  A must see!
